title: LF team - Challenger support main
body:
IGN: Eyla

Hey guys, I'm a support main currently in challenger (342LP) and am looking for a team (high diamond - challenger) that is looking to play in tournaments. Don't have much experience in playing in a team but can learn fast. Available to play after school hours and weekends. Have skype/ts/other comms.

Please add me in game to discuss more!
